Package: milt
Title: Modern Integrated Library for Timeseries
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gideon", "Nti Boateng",
                   email = "gidiboateng200@gmail.com",
                   role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A unified framework for time series forecasting, anomaly
    detection, classification, and analysis in R. Provides a consistent API
    across classical statistical models, machine learning, and deep learning
    approaches. Includes backtesting, pipeline construction, multi-series
    support, and model explainability.
